{"tid":1492061,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"連尼住巴打請入！！！整app保障手足安全！！！","createTime":"2019-08-20T16:08:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T04:06:58.000Z","uid":204565,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ca4ee90f4e49c4e07113d7cc4b0bc0852d821c92","tid":1492061,"uid":204565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:08:39.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">鑒於呢排好多黑社會斬人同藍屍亂打人既問題，啲狗又唔會去處理。希望利用app去保障大家安全。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: gold;\">因為缺乏server所以想請求連尼住巴打幫手</span></ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">整app概念：</span></span></strong><br />\n1.將網上即時地圖變成app<br />\n2.手足可以在地圖上放任務，例如起連儂牆，或快閃等(*需要有片或相，突發事情除外)<br />\n3.在地圖上亦可標示邊到有狗or狗車，水馬，有黑社會<br />\n4.任務亦可以set時間及時間<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">好處：</span></strong><br />\n1.偵測狗在何處<br />\n2.實時知道各處訊息<br />\n3.保護手足安全<br />\n4.發生突發在附近亦可幫手<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">問題：</span><br />\n1.放流料由於手足放任務需要post相，及手足可以以街坊or行街經過，以避開狗查截。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求各位手足幫手推比連尼住睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a600f2bb126196ab35f5ace5a3141fe2abe979d","tid":1492061,"uid":204565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:08:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f83c67ec02dfe1e0a17ab6ae4bc7992e510a5d83","tid":1492061,"uid":204565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:09:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8d13b690d148812658159d4e8f144a8dba00f1ae","tid":1492061,"uid":204565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:09:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8fcde2c9ff2f38de37e0ee8422cbece22e32342c","tid":1492061,"uid":2562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:09:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PXcMrux.jpg\" 